{"tid":523423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片為證) 大陸比香港更開放?","createTime":"2018-01-08T14:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T06:21:51.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8cdd4b448db7b71a34b9a25c285d2c7de9699e","tid":523423,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"我係指演藝界既性感尺度方面.  政府審查尺度方面, 香港尺度當然遠遠比大陸開放.  反而大陸不乏演藝人好勇於挑戰底線, 至少比TVB勇敢得多.<br />\n<br />\n好似王子文咁, 係大陸係好出名既電視花旦.  但佢依然夠膽係《追凶者也》中接近全裸地去演出扑野戲. 雖然段戲拍完後, 比官方cut到剩番十幾秒, 但出到黎既片段, 依然有肉地同激過《喜愛夜蒲》, 《私人會所》, 《PG戀愛指引》之流. (扑野片段由3:45開始)  <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av14137217/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav14137217%2F&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6053c917\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av14137217/</a><br />\n如果王子文係TVB藝員, 恐怕早被封殺.  (好似蔣家旻係《第一次不是你》露下背, 都比TVB冷藏一排.)<br />\n<br />\n當然, 勇敢既大陸演員唔只王子文一個.  連大姐大范冰冰都曾經係《二次曝光》半裸演出, 露波形兼(著住內褲)露股形. (半裸片段係18:30開始).<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x2gtw1n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymotion.com%2Fvideo%2Fx2gtw1n&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=872e5e21\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x2gtw1n</a><br />\n<br />\n係影雜誌相方面, 唔少大陸演員亦比較大膽.  好似大姐大李冰冰上年幫雜誌影公益全裸照<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170926/1211555/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170926%2F1211555%2F&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=25402193\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170926%2F1211555%2F&h=bee4e471\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170926/1211555/</a><br />\n<br />\n而剛憑《羞羞的鐵拳》成為19億票房女星既馬麗, 亦剛為男人裝拍性感照show股形.  係「限奶令」下, 如果TVB藝員拍呢d尺度既照片, 　肯定被炒魷. <br />\n<a href=\"http://slide.ent.sina.com.cn/star/slide_4_704_262982.html?from=sinahomepage#p=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fslide.ent.sina.com.cn%2Fstar%2Fslide_4_704_262982.html%3Ffrom%3Dsinahomepage%23p%3D1&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3918a9f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://slide.ent.sina.com.cn/star/slide_4_704_262982.html?from=sinahomepage#p=1</a><br />\n<br />\n無錯, 大陸電影同劇集好多都係垃圾. 但亦有唔少大陸人係勇於踩界同挑戰底線, 比一d純奶共既香港行內人更有良心.  回望香港, 好似TVB咁不斷自我河蟹, 兼限制旗下藝員, 就真係令人嘆息.  王祖藍話TVB制肘比大陸更大, 其實唔係無道理.<br />\n<br />\n(當然, 都有d香港行內人唔係純奶共, 比較有良心.)"},{"pid":"b5ba6e137b4b582f7d28d58abe7c9437ec3180aa","tid":523423,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ab44a81ebc455100ccd51f37067aa42f896dd09","tid":523423,"uid":58862,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5ba6e137b4b582f7d28d58abe7c9437ec3180aa","tid":523423,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"香港女演員唔係雞？"},{"pid":"3ef88978b59847edaad099b80bd526864149946a","tid":523423,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab44a81ebc455100ccd51f37067aa42f896dd09","tid":523423,"uid":58862,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5ba6e137b4b582f7d28d58abe7c9437ec3180aa","tid":523423,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"香港女演員唔係雞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"e04462c649335d0094bda8410f749d1a919a9a44","tid":523423,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:27:26.000Z","msg":"一早知<br />\n以前廣體播英超上面有condom廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8574e5c4d2eee6139a14bfaa33bfbe4f406b857","tid":523423,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"呢 d 唔係叫開放，呢 d 叫不知廉恥，道德淪亡"}]}